        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Technora Survival Cord by ASR Tactical may not look like much, but could help save your life!<br><br>While it is quite thin with a diameter of only .08\", it has a breaking strength of 450 lbs. This cord is made of Technora, which is an abrasion-resistant, low stretch, high strength material. It also has a PTFE (Teflon) coating, which increases the abrasion resistance and adds UV protection.<br><br>It weighs barely more than an ounce and takes up little space, so it is a must-have for your survival kit!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
